'''Azrf g twnnaḍt idusn''' (s [[Tutlayt Tanglizt|tanglizt]] : '''right to a healthy environment''') iga yan uzrf sg izrfan n ufgan, azrf ad ar isawwal f uzrf n ufgan g twnnaḍt, tawnnaḍt [[Tadusi|tadusant]] nɣ tawnnaḍt idusn ifulkin. Acku kudd afgan ila azrf ad, azrf g tudrt idusn d azrf g twnnaḍt idusn. Azrf ad ur illi g ma izrin, acku awal f imrsi ad n twnnaḍt iga amaynu g umaḍal nnaɣ, ikka ad imrsi ad dar timsmunin d imussutn iswwrayn d ar sawwaln f [[twnnaḍt]] d izrfan d kullu ma srs izdin.

Awal f [[Izrfan|uzrf]] ad ur illi sg ma yad izrin, acku imrsi ad n twnnaḍt iga amaynu, issnta wawwal f imrsi ad sg ugraw n Stukhulm g usggas n 1972. 

Azrf ad izdi d tugt n iztfan yaḍni, zund ukan azrf g waman, d azrf g ucci, d uzrf g usslmd ...

